{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/til/technical-writing/one/06-lists-and-tables-1/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"bestalign's dev blog","categories":[{"displayText":"홈","priority":0,"name":"home","url":"/"},{"displayText":"TIL","priority":1,"name":"til","url":"/til"},{"displayText":"개발","priority":2,"name":"dev","url":"/dev"},{"displayText":"독서","priority":3,"name":"reading","url":"/reading"},{"displayText":"번역","priority":4,"name":"translation","url":"/translation"},{"displayText":"일기","priority":5,"name":"everydaylife","url":"/everydaylife"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"fd4b67cd-7c98-5076-897b-abb75bc2816d","excerpt":"적절한 리스트 종류를 선택하라 다음의 리스트 종류가 있다: bullted list numbered list embedded list 리스트에 순서가 있다면 numbered list를, 순서가 없다면 bulleted list를 사용하라. embedded list…","html":"<h4 id=\"적절한-리스트-종류를-선택하라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%A0%88%ED%95%9C-%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%EC%A2%85%EB%A5%98%EB%A5%BC-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%ED%95%98%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"적절한 리스트 종류를 선택하라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적절한 리스트 종류를 선택하라</h4>\n<p>다음의 리스트 종류가 있다:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bullted list</li>\n<li>numbered list</li>\n<li>embedded list</li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n<p>리스트에 순서가 있다면 numbered list를, 순서가 없다면 bulleted list를 사용하라.</p>\n<p>embedded list는 다음의 예제처럼 문장 내에 포함되는 리스트이다.</p>\n<p>e.g. The llamacatcher API enables callers to create and query llamas, analyze alpacas, delete vicugnas, and track dromedaries.</p>\n<p>embedded list는 기술 문서에서는 추천하지 않는다. 가능하면 bulleted list나 numbered list로 바꾸어라.</p>\n<h4 id=\"리스트-아이템의-스타일을-같게-유지하라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%EC%95%84%EC%9D%B4%ED%85%9C%EC%9D%98-%EC%8A%A4%ED%83%80%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EA%B0%99%EA%B2%8C-%EC%9C%A0%EC%A7%80%ED%95%98%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"리스트 아이템의 스타일을 같게 유지하라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>리스트 아이템의 스타일을 같게 유지하라</h4>\n<p>다음의 스타일을 같게 유지해야 한다:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>grammar</li>\n<li>logical category</li>\n<li>capitalization</li>\n<li>punctuation</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>carrots</li>\n<li>potatos</li>\n<li>cabbages</li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>Carrots contain lots of Vitamin A.</li>\n<li>Potatos taste delicious.</li>\n<li>Cabbages provide oodles of Vitamin K.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"numbered-list의-아이템은-명령형으로-써라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#numbered-list%EC%9D%98-%EC%95%84%EC%9D%B4%ED%85%9C%EC%9D%80-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%ED%98%95%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%8D%A8%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"numbered list의 아이템은 명령형으로 써라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>numbered list의 아이템은 명령형으로 써라</h4>\n<p>numbered list는 여러 행동들을 열거 할 때 많이 사용한다. 그럴 경우, 각 아이템을 명령형으로 써라.</p>\n<h4 id=\"마침표를-올바르게-사용하라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EC%B9%A8%ED%91%9C%EB%A5%BC-%EC%98%AC%EB%B0%94%EB%A5%B4%EA%B2%8C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"마침표를 올바르게 사용하라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>마침표를 올바르게 사용하라</h4>\n<p>리스트 아이템이 문장일 경우 대문자로 시작하고 마침표로 끝내라. 그게 아니라면 소문자로 시작하고 마침표는 제외하라.</p>\n<h4 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/tech-writing/one/lists-and-tables\">Google Dev Technical Writing 1 - Lists and Tables</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Lists and Tables 1","category":"til","date":"July 03, 2021","updated":null,"description":null,"tags":["technical writing"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/technical-writing/one/05-short-sentence-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Short Sentence 2"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/technical-writing/one/07-lists-and-tables-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Lists and Tables 2"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"fd4b67cd-7c98-5076-897b-abb75bc2816d","previousPostId":"1089e10e-74aa-5c15-9e9b-979b369b8c02","nextPostId":"c1ef68ac-fea7-574a-8315-1da393387e16"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"]}